OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774048278
OL,3,CGuernsey to introduce UK-style MOT
OL,4,Ctests
OL,6,FThe States of Guernsey will publish
OL,7,Fnew proposals to roll out MOT-style
OL,8,Ftests across the island.
OL,10,FThe Committee for Environment and
OL,11,FInfrastructure (E&I) says its
OL,12,F'periodic technical inspection' scheme
OL,13,Fwill start in phases - beginning with
OL,14,Fvehicles between 20 and 40 years old
OL,15,Fand those that regularly travel abroad.
OL,17,FAround 14,000 vehicles will be
OL,18,Faffected by the first phase - but in
OL,19,Ftime, nearly every car and van will
OL,20,Fneed to be checked, which has left
OL,21,Fsome concerned.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
