OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774048278
OL,3,CGuernsey to introduce UK-style MOT
OL,4,Ctests
OL,6,FWith more than 90,000 cars registered
OL,7,Fin Guernsey, the Committee wants to
OL,8,Fensure they are safe and roadworthy,
OL,9,Fwhich can prove a tough task for the
OL,10,FStates.
OL,12,FHowever, much of the detail around
OL,13,Fcost and how often it will have to
OL,14,Ftake place remains unclear.
OL,16,FIn addition, rising petrol prices
OL,17,Fafter the conflict in the Middle East
OL,18,Fare causing motorists to question
OL,19,Fwhether they will have to shoulder
OL,20,Fadditional financial burdens.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
