FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774048278
OL,3,CGuernsey to introduce UK-style MOT
OL,4,Ctests
OL,6,FMechanic Paul Le Breton says
OL,7,Fintroducing standardised vehicle
OL,8,Finspections is long overdue.
OL,10,F"We have around ten or so cars in on a
OL,11,Fday-to-day basis. Some of them are in
OL,12,Fpretty bad conditions. Where we see it
OL,13,Fis where cars haven't been serviced or
OL,14,Fmaintained," Paul explains.
OL,16,F"Possibly, people have bought the
OL,17,Fvehicle from an independent seller or
OL,18,Foff the side of a road, and it hasn't
OL,19,Fhad an inspection carried out at all."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774048278
OL,3,CGuernsey to introduce UK-style MOT
OL,4,Ctests
OL,6,FThe tests will be conducted by
OL,7,Fgarages, but it will be up to the
OL,8,FStates to oversee the inspections.
OL,10,FHowever, Paul thinks that the price
OL,11,Fwill not parallel UK MOT pricing.
OL,13,FWith fuel duty increasing again in
OL,14,F2025 - to 90p per litre - even more
OL,15,Fdrivers may feel the squeeze.
OL,17,F"My belief is that it will be more
OL,18,Fexpensive than the UK, purely for the
OL,19,Ffact that it's more expensive to
OL,20,Foperate out of Guernsey anyway," Paul
OL,21,Fadded.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774048278
OL,3,CGuernsey to introduce UK-style MOT
OL,4,Ctests
OL,6,FITV News spoke to Guernsey residents
OL,7,Fwho were unsure whether the island had
OL,8,Fissues with faulty cars, and were also
OL,9,Fconcerned about whether law changes
OL,10,Fwould overreach.
OL,12,FOne motorist said: "I get the logic
OL,13,Fbehind it; you do need something to
OL,14,Fregulate the condition of vehicles on
OL,15,Fthe roads, but I question what the
OL,16,Fcost will be."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
