FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1774048278
OL,3,CGuernsey to introduce UK-style MOT
OL,4,Ctests
OL,6,FDeputy Adrian Gabriel, the President
OL,7,Fof E&I, told ITV News in a statement:
OL,8,F"Officers are working through items,
OL,9,Fsuch as the preparation of technical
OL,10,Fspecification checklists and manuals.
OL,12,F"Once this work has been done, a
OL,13,Fpolicy letter will be submitted to the
OL,14,FStates, setting out the proposed dates
OL,15,Ffor introduction."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
